<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Hear my voice, God, listen to my complaint;</para>

<para style="q1">preserve my life from fear of my enemies.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Hide me from the secret plotting of evildoers,</para>

<para style="q1">from the commotion of the doers of iniquity.</para>
